OL,5, Antisemitic hate crimes rose sharply in
OL,6, the month after the Hamas attack on    
OL,7, Israel, figures from some of the UK's  
OL,8, largest police forces suggest.         
OL,10,FSome forces also recorded a rise in    
OL,11,FIslamophobic offences, though the      
OL,12,Fpicture is more mixed.                 
OL,14,FThe Community Safety Trust, a Jewish   
OL,15,Fcharity, has called the figures        
OL,16,F"shocking".                            
OL,18,FMeanwhile, campaigners against         
OL,19,Fanti-Muslim abuse have described them  
OL,20,Fas "deeply worrying".                  
